---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Angela McCann | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Angela McCann, Licensed Assistant at Heidi Blondin Financial. Over 15 years of customer service and banking experience, dedicated to exceptional client care."
>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 items-start">

        <div class="md:col-span-1">
          <img
            src="/team/angela-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Angela McCann — Licensed Assistant, Heidi Blondin Financial"
            class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top"
          />
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-xl text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Angela McCann</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Licensed Assistant</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-5">
            <p>Angela joined Heidi Blondin Financial in August 2017 as Client Care Coordinator, bringing with her over 15 years of customer service and banking experience. Known for her warm approach and dedication to client care, Angela is passionate about helping others and ensuring every client feels supported and valued.</p>
            <p>She completed her Mutual Fund course in January 2017 and is currently working toward her Life Insurance Qualification, eager to expand her financial expertise and continue delivering exceptional service.</p>
            <p>Angela holds a Social Services Diploma from Loyalist College and has also studied Behaviour Science at St. Lawrence College, giving her a strong foundation in understanding and supporting client needs.</p>
            <p>When she's not hard at work supporting clients, Angela enjoys spending quality time with her husband James and their two daughters. She loves being outdoors—whether it's boating, swimming, or camping. You'll often find her relaxing with a good book on the deck, soaking up the sunshine and fresh air.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/heidi/" class="font-sans text-sm font-medium text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700">← Back to the team</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
